 |dead-url     = no
}}{{en}}</ref>

1985至1988年任[[劍橋大學菲茨威廉學院|劍橋大學菲茨威廉學院]]東方研究院（現名為「亞洲和中東研究」）漢學教授（2008年改名{{link-en|李約瑟漢學講座教授|Joseph Needham Professorship of Chinese History, Science, and Civilization}}）。<ref name="香港中文大學"/><ref>{{Cite web| url=http://www.fitz.cam.ac.uk/academic/courses/asian-and-middle-eastern-studies| title=''Asian and Middle Eastern Studies''| publisher=[[劍橋大學菲茨威廉學院|劍橋大學菲茨威廉學院]]| access-date=2014-01-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116133411/http://www.fitz.cam.ac.uk/academic/courses/asian-and-middle-eastern-studies| archive-date=2014-01-16| dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal| title=劍橋漢學的形成與發展| author=闕維民| journal=漢學研究通訊| volume=21| issue=1| orig-year=民國91年2月| date=2002-02| page=42| url=http://www.ames.cam.ac.uk/~rs10009/p031-043.pdf| format=PDF| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116133413/http://www.ames.cam.ac.uk/~rs10009/p031-043.pdf| archivedate=2014-01-16}}</ref>

